title: -Studies of Excitation Cross Sections of (N,N`G) Reactions.-

x4codes.shortRef: Rept: Japanese report to EANDC, No.5S (1965)

x4freetext: JAERI 5.5 MV VAN DE GRAAFF ACCELERATOR.
LONG COUNTER FOR NEUTRON MONITOR, AND
PROPORTIONAL COUNTER FILLED WITH METHANE GAS
WERE USED IN THE ABSOLUTE MEASUREMENTS OF FLUX.
A.P.T. JAPAN CODE CHANGED TO JPN
CORRECTION OF ABSORPTION OF GAMMA-RAYS PRODUCED
IN THE SAMPLE WAS EXPERIMENTALLY DETERMINED, AND
CORRECTION FOR FINITE ANGULAR RESOLUTION WAS NOT DONE
SOME CASES, HOWEVER, NO ERRORS ARE GIVEN.
